nages our travel logistics, medical visa fast-tracking coordination, and hotel/airport transfer managers globally.</p></div><div class=\"text-teal-700 text-4xs font-bold mt-4 flex items-center justify-end\">Show bio ▼</div></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer bg-slate-50 border rounded-3xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 reveal border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 shadow-xs\" style=\"transition-delay:300ms\"><div class=\"relative aspect-square bg-slate-200 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Mr. Sandeep Verma\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 25vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D400%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm\">Mr. Sandeep Verma</h3><p class=\"text-teal-700 text-2xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-1\">India Network Director</p><div class=\"transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden max-h-0 opacity-0\"><p class=\"text-4xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-200 pt-3\">Based in New Delhi, Sandeep coordinates directly with Fortis, Apollo, Medanta, and other tertiary partner hospital desks to support priority booking and patient arrival reception.</p></div><div class=\"text-teal-700 text-4xs font-bold mt-4 flex items-center justify-end\">Show bio ▼</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 py-20 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-800 to-cyan-950 px-8 py-16 text-center text-white shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden reveal transition duration-700 ease-out transform opacity-0 translate-y-4\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_75%_20%,rgba(20,184,166,0.15),transparent_25%)]\"></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold mb-4 relative z-10\">We Are Ready to Help You</h2><p class=\"text-slate-200 text-sm max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8 relative z-10\">For nearly two decades, we have supported patients from Bangladesh and other countries in accessing treatment across India. Reach out for a private consultation review.</p><button class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-white text-teal-900 font-bold px-8 py-4 shadow-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition cursor-pointer relative z-10\">Start Your Care Journey</button></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-slate-950 text-slate-300\"><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-5 py-14 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] lg:px-8\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-white\"><span class=\"grid size-10 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-teal-500 text-xl font-black\">✚</span><strong class=\"font-display\">Shifa Global Care</strong></div><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-sm text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Advancing Healthcare. Building Trust. Transforming Lives.<!-- --> We help international patients navigate treatment in India with clarity, dignity, and ongoing support.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Explore</h2><div class=\"mt-4 grid gap-3 text-sm\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/services\">Services</a><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/treatments\">Treatments</a><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/hospitals\">Hospitals</a></div></div><div><h2 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Patient support</h2><div class=\"mt-4 grid gap-3 text-sm\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/medical-visa\">Medical visa</a><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/faq\">Frequently asked questions</a><a class=\"hover:text-teal-300\" href=\"/contact\">Contact care team</a></div></div><div><h2 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-white\">Important note</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Shifa coordinates care but does not replace advice from a licensed clinician. For urgent symptoms, seek local emergency care.</p></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-white/10\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-5 text-xs text-slate-500 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between lg:px-8\"><span>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Shifa Global Care Solution Lim